links.description: AllianceBernstein preliminary assets under management of $631B at Sept. 30, 2020 decreased from $643B at Aug. 31, 2020. links.title: $AB AB Announces September 30, 2020 Assets Under Management
links.description: NEW YORK, Oct. 12, 2020 /PRNewswire/ -- AllianceBernstein L.P. ("AB") and AllianceBernstein Holding L.P. ("AB Holding") (NYSE: AB) today announced that preliminary assets under management decreased to $631 billion during September 2020 from $643 billion at the end of August. The 1.9% decrease was due primarily to market depreciation, and to a lesser extent, firmwide net outflows.
